nf_ingredient_statement: Whole Grain Oats, Sugar, Oat Bran, Whole Grain Wheat, Brown Rice Syrup, Honey, Brown Sugar Syrup, Rice Flour, Corn Starch, Salt, Canola and/Or Rice Bran Oil, Natural Flavor, Tripotassium Phosphate, Barley Malt Extract, Natural Almond Flavor, Color Added. Vitamin E (Mixed Tocopherols) Added to Preserve Freshness. Vitamins and Minerals: Calcium Carbonate, Zinc and Iron (Mineral Nutrients), Vitamin C (Sodium Ascorbate), A B Vitamin (Niacinamide), Vitamin B1 (Thiamin Mononitrate), Vitamin B6 (Pyridoxine Hydrochloride), Vitamin B2 (Riboflavin), Vitamin A (Palmitate), A B Vitamin (Folic Acid), Vitamin B12, Vitamin D3. Contains Wheat and Almond Ingredients.
